{"tid":960254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇糖兄妹再合體？🙄","createTime":"2018-12-29T09:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T10:41:05.000Z","uid":44730,"like":94,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0cea62d19f011e27926273154f73dae2844d0b","tid":960254,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:08:23.000Z","msg":"但下年仲有冇機會見到 HMV 標貼  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"999aeeefd676e5f1d781db46aeb425c8c0cfcaa6","tid":960254,"uid":44730,"like":61,"dislike":5,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"二人組合糖兄妹潘雲峰（糖兄）和黃山怡（糖妹）前晚在旺角朗豪坊舉行音樂表演，兩人分開三年後再度合體，糖妹說：「出年係我哋成軍十周年，所以今次特登返嚟呢度演出，因為當年我哋就係喺度被發掘。」他們表示明年會再以糖兄妹方式出新歌。<br />\n<br />\n糖兄妹表示多年來看着一班樂迷成長：「佢哋細細個就聽我哋啲歌，𠵱家都結埋婚生埋仔，希望佢哋啲仔女都做埋我哋fans。」糖兄透露新歌已經做好，等拍完MV預計明年二月面世。至於會否同期出實體碟及開騷？糖妹說：「開騷當然想啦，出碟就要睇情況，希望造多幾首歌先。」"},{"pid":"25c325a8c7966d84dd09cff159da565d3dc322fe","tid":960254,"uid":60092,"like":409,"dislike":5,"score":404,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"撈唔掂又痴返去糖兄到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02f56b5a81e2947ef742089f4a6a6aee4255c6c","tid":960254,"uid":132587,"like":700,"dislike":5,"score":695,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/346962/org/3205aad468de4cc15f927845744f04db.jpg/83qSTapWVglploxtkpgR-p54RnD9zvGJDYKV9w2Clfc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F346962%2Forg%2F3205aad468de4cc15f927845744f04db.jpg%2F83qSTapWVglploxtkpgR-p54RnD9zvGJDYKV9w2Clfc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8b15071b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0cca2061288f96217f6b932449127abe444a080","tid":960254,"uid":36084,"like":195,"dislike":1,"score":194,"c